# Regenerated binary artifacts from the ASITIC binary
# (CIF, GDS, S2P, raw analysis logs). The JSON ground truth in
# tests/data/validation/ stays tracked, but the per-shape layouts
# and per-case analysis bundles are derivative outputs of the
# UC-Berkeley-licensed binary and are reproduced on demand by
# scripts/regen_validation_artifacts.py in the parent asitic-re
# repo. See TESTSET.md there for the workflow.
tests/data/validation/layouts/
tests/data/validation/analysis/
